      <title>巴西干旱天气推迟农作物播种，大豆期货上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/soy-futures-rise-as-dry-weather-delays-crop-seeding-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[天气预报显示巴西降雨较少，干旱导致新大豆作物播种季节推迟，大豆期货价格上涨。]]></description>
